{"noun":[{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/1d/85/17529_crt_0dRZE.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/1d/85/17529_crt_0dRZE.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/1d/85/17529_crt_0dRZE.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/1d/85/17529_crt_0dRZE.jpg"},"name":"モブキャラクター","summary":"闲角，常称作路人，在电视剧、电影等作品中，指戏份薄弱的副角、不相关的小人物、串场的闲杂人等。可能用来表达地方民众的声音，或是充当背景。\r\nモブキャラクター（mob character）とは、漫画、アニメ、映画、コンピュータゲームなどに描かれる端役のこと。群衆（群集）、または主要キャラクター以外の、その他大勢のこと。群集キャラ、背景キャラともいう。","relation":"闲角","actors":[{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/44/02/31832_prsn_I0k2g.jpg?r=1517908602","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/44/02/31832_prsn_I0k2g.jpg?r=1517908602","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/44/02/31832_prsn_I0k2g.jpg?r=1517908602","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/44/02/31832_prsn_I0k2g.jpg?r=1517908602"},"name":"町山芹菜","short_summary":"AIR AGENCY所属\r\n\r\n出身地：千葉県\r\n趣味：掃除 、映像鑑賞 、お菓子作り\r\n特技： 人の顔を覚えること\r\n卒業養成機関：日本ナレーション演技研究所\r\nAIR AGENCY声優養成所","career":["seiyu"],"id":31832,"type":1,"locked":false},{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/f1/cd/50371_prsn_8UCuk.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/f1/cd/50371_prsn_8UCuk.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/f1/cd/50371_prsn_8UCuk.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/f1/cd/50371_prsn_8UCuk.jpg"},"name":"大木咲絵子","short_summary":"大泽事务所所属。\r\nアニメ\r\n「可愛いだけじゃない式守さん」\r\n「トモダチゲーム」\r\n「ちみも」\r\n「可愛いだけじゃない式守さん」\r\n「ＣＵＥ！」\r\n\r\nゲーム\r\n「白猫プロジェクト」サーシャ、フィーネ","career":["seiyu"],"id":50371,"type":1,"locked":false},{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/b1/5a/65241_prsn_8mPas.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/b1/5a/65241_prsn_8mPas.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/b1/5a/65241_prsn_8mPas.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/b1/5a/65241_prsn_8mPas.jpg"},"name":"村上麻衣","short_summary":"出身地：福岡県\r\n使える方言：筑豊弁\r\n趣味：絵を描く、ものまね、ゲーム、ホラー映画鑑賞、Live2Dモデリング\r\n特技：絵を描く、そろばん(初段)\r\n卒業養成機関：福岡スクールオブミュージック専